title: First Look at Uncharted Movie! - Kinda Funny Games Daily 10.22.20
description:
Thank you, Old Spice!  Try Old Spice Below Deck.  Available in the Family Planning Aisle at Walmart or online at http://Walmart.com/oldspicebelowdeck

Tim and Greg check out our first look at Tom Holland as Nathan Drake, discuss Nintendo's bizarre release plans, go over multiple game upgrade plans, and more!
